data.description: Unique 2-2.5-2 showplace designed w-meticulous attention to detail & extraordinary amenities. Vaulted Aspen wood ceilings & high end wood floors dominate the entry. Liv boasts stone design WBFP & lots of windows for natural light. Open to gourmet kitchen w-island & bar seating.Main bdrm is down & offers private bath. Opportunity upstairs for 2 bdrms or gameroom w- access to office area. Shaded dual outdoor living areas & outdoor kitchen is sure to combine pleasure & fun to this outstanding natural setting. Added attraction is ability to dry dock seadoos & boat right at the dock. Nice size shop for storing all the needed lake items or turn it into a party barn w-bonus safe room already in place.Great waterfront!
